{"tid":2034372,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"主子成日係貓砂盆出邊屙屎，崩潰","createTime":"2020-05-25T08:00:13.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-26T04:08:28.000Z","uid":266003,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"6e07031406a3a04445332100f43f143640df720f","tid":2034372,"uid":266003,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T08:00:13.000Z","msg":"呢隻英短已經養左差唔多半年,一直都係砂盤大小便,各樣野一直冇變過(砂盤位置,貓砂,貓糧等).但係近呢幾個月唔知點解,好鍾意係正砂盤出口對開位置屙屎,用過urine off,又試過移動砂盤,都係唔得.<br />\n<br />\n佢頭先又屙左係出面,屙咁多次又唔係屙爛屎喎,健康又唔係有事,所以真係好頭痛.而家屋企係鋪木地板嘅,唔知關唔關事,D味可能抹唔走.係嘅話都幾麻煩,因為我要搵屋搬,大部分我睇過嘅都係鋪木地板.<br />\n<br />\n希望各位可以幫下我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bW7Qf2R.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbW7Qf2R.jpg&h=5e487bc2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"23f33a39810ae41d571e945221735c850d0e8187","tid":2034372,"uid":260749,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T08:02:02.000Z","msg":"我都有地下條魚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d9630151f5dcd9665ec0289922ae0cf41666ae0","tid":2034372,"uid":266003,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"23f33a39810ae41d571e945221735c850d0e8187","tid":2034372,"uid":260749,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T08:02:02.000Z","msg":"我都有地下條魚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T08:07:53.000Z","msg":"佢玩左一兩次唔玩<img src=\"/